Title: The Bee | New Gold
Body (HTML):
Introducing The Bee.
Plain. Simple. True.
A reminder of these simple truths:

Be Grateful: “Gratitude comes from actively remembering God and His goodness.”
Be Smart: “Educate your minds and hands to be an influence for good.”
Be Clean: In language, in thought, in body, in dress.
Be True: “Be loyal, be faithful and be true to your own convictions.”
Be Humble: “Esteem others as ourselves and lift them as high or higher than we are.”
Be Prayerful: “You need His help, and you know that you need His help.”

“Go forward in life with a twinkle in your eye and a smile on your face, but with strong purpose in your heart.”
-President Gordon B. Hinckley

Give this necklace to yourself or someone you love to remind them how to 🐝 to find happiness. This necklace looks so cute layered with our “Marjorie” necklace

Our Bee necklace is on our olive 18 inch chain.

Introducing The Bee.
Plain. Simple. True.
A reminder of these simple truths:

Be Grateful: “Gratitude comes from actively remembering God and His goodness.”
Be Smart: “Educate your minds and hands to be an influence for good.”
Be Clean: In language, in thought, in body, in dress.
Be True: “Be loyal, be faithful and be true to your own convictions.”
Be Humble: “Esteem others as ourselves and lift them as high or higher than we are.”
Be Prayerful: “You need His help, and you know that you need His help.”

“Go forward in life with a twinkle in your eye and a smile on your face, but with strong purpose in your heart.”
-President Gordon B. Hinckley
